data.description: Welcome to Your Country Retreat at 7672 Togoodoo Rd!Embrace the tranquility and freedom of country living with this spacious 2001 detitled mobile home, perfectly nestled on an expansive 3.77-acre lot. Ideal for those who love the outdoors and seek a private, serene lifestyle, 7672 Togoodoo Rd offers a unique blend of comfort and convenience.Step into a generously sized layout that provides ample room for relaxation, entertainment, and family life. The home's open design ensures that each space feels connected while still offering distinct areas for living, dining, and more.Located just 2 miles from Togoodoo Boat Ramp and 7 miles from Dawhoo Boat Ramp, this property is a dream come true for boating and fishing enthusiasts. Imagine easy access to weekends on the water or tranquil evenings enjoying nature's beauty this location makes it all possible!  The 3.77-acre lot not only ensures privacy but also offers endless possibilities for gardening, hobbies, or simply enjoying the vast outdoor space. It's an ideal setting for those who desire room to roam and appreciate nature's peacefulness.  While you'll love the seclusion and quiet that 7672 Togoodoo Rd offers, you won't have to sacrifice convenience. This property is situated in a community that enjoys easy access to local amenities, ensuring that everything you need is within reach. It's the perfect balance of rural charm and accessibility!  If you're looking for a spacious home with plenty of outdoor space and easy access to water activities, then this property fits the glove perfectly!  Contact us today to schedule a viewing and see how this property can fulfill your desire for a peaceful, spacious home."
